              <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Note:<\/strong> Even if you don&#x2019;t want to cycle, the city is very pedestrian-friendly. Most of the city center is traffic-free, which makes it great for exploring as a traveler!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28123949\/la-rochelle-france-8-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"61995\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28123949\/la-rochelle-france-8.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=61995\" class=\"wp-image-61995 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28123949\/la-rochelle-france-8-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28123949\/la-rochelle-france-8-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28123949\/la-rochelle-france-8-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28123949\/la-rochelle-france-8-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28123949\/la-rochelle-france-8-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28123949\/la-rochelle-france-8-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltin