terest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28133125\/la-rochelle-france-2-1-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28133125\/la-rochelle-france-2-1-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"La Rochelle, France: Best Things To Do in the City of Sailing\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-visit-the-town-hall\">Visit the Town Hall&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The town hall of La Rochelle is an ornate building and one of the most eye-catching parts of town. Build in the 17th century; it&#x2019;s thought to be one of the oldest town halls in the whole of France (that&#x2019;s still used for its original purpose)! It looks more like a palace than a town hall, with its detailed carvings, white pillars, turrets, and watchtower. The town hall is a great spot to start your discovery of the old quarter.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><b>Also read: <\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/paris-city-trip-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A 3-day city trip in Paris<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4.jpg\" alt=\"la rochelle france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"239\" height=\"338\" alt=\"la rochelle france\" class=\"wp-image-61901 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1355px) 100vw, 1355px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4.jpg 1355w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-423x600.jpg 423w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-572x810.jpg 572w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-239x338.jpg 239w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-127x180.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-542x768.jpg 542w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-723x1024.jpg 723w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-762x1080.jpg 762w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-1016x1440.jpg 1016w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27123609\/la-rochelle-france-4-300x425.jpg 300w, https:\/\/