2004 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1335px) 100vw, 1335px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12.jpg 1335w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-417x600.jpg 417w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-563x810.jpg 563w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-235x338.jpg 235w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-113x163.jpg 113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-125x180.jpg 125w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-534x768.jpg 534w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-712x1024.jpg 712w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-751x1080.jpg 751w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-1001x1440.jpg 1001w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-300x431.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-600x863.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124034\/la-rochelle-france-12.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-explore-the-beaches\">Explore the Beaches<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>La Rochelle&#x2019;s position on the west coast means it&#x2019;s home to loads of beautiful beaches for exploring and relaxing. The cliffs are popular amongst walkers, with many of the coastal walks starting here.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Plage des Minimes<\/strong><br>Plage des Minimes is a long white stretch of sand, just walking distance from La Rochelle. It&#x2019;s perfect for a day of collecting shells and paddling in the ocean. Afterward, walk up onto the cliffs for beautiful sunset views, followed by some delicious locally caught seafood in the restaurants.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Plage de la Concurrence<\/strong><br>Plage de la Concurrence is 10 minutes from the port of La Rochelle. You can get great views of the La Lanterne tower from here. It&#x2019;s also super convenient as it&#x2019;s closest to the town.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Chef de Baie<\/strong><br>This small sandy beach is a great one to explore on a trip to La Rochelle. To the side is an area where you can kayak, and it&#x2019;s also the starting point for a clifftop walk. Additionally, there&#x2019;s a lifeguard who supervises swimming, so it&#x2019;s great for families.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Also see: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-la-rochelle\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">all the hotel options in this city<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__wrapper video-block__wrapper--breakout\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/VideoObject\">\n                <h3 class=\"video-block__wrapper-title\" itemprop=\"name\">South-West France<\/h3>\n\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnail\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/03110839\/sw-france-cover-2-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"South-West France\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/03110839\/sw-france-cover-2-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2021-07-31 11:06:09\">\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block video-block--mediavine\">\n                    <div class=\"video-block__embed\">\n                        <div class=\"mv-video-target mv-video-id-ojki2coomgfe2fypr03z\" data-video-id=\"ojki2coomgfe2fypr03z\" data-volume=\"70\" data-ratio=\"16:9\" data-autoinsert=\"true\" data-disable-jsonld=\"true\"><\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <a class=\"video-block__credit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/c\/saltinourhair?sub_confirmation=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"YouTube Salt in our Hair\">\n                    <div class=\"socials__item\">\n                        <span class=\"socials__link\">\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-youtube\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-youtube\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <span>Subscribe to our <b>YouT