>Bordeaux<\/a>, you can reach La Rochelle by direct train in just 3 hours. The ticket price varies but is between 50-80 EUR. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/trains-to-la-rochelle-fr\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book well in advance to get a better price<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>By Car: <\/strong>Paris to La Rochelle is just under 5 hours. <meta charset=\"utf-8\">Rent a car at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>, they work with local car rental companies. When booking through Sunny Cars, all insurances are included. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book your local rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>By Plane:<\/strong> La Rochelle has an international airport close to the city offering flights to other popular destinations in Europe. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-around\">Getting Around<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>La Rochelle is a relatively small city, and it&#x2019;s very walkable. If you want to explore nature outside of the city or see the island of Ile de Re, we recommend hiring a car. However, be aware that islands like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/aix-island-rochefort\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ile d&#x2019;Aix<\/a> are transport-free and can be explored only by bike or walking.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28124044\/la-rochelle-france-13.jpg\" alt=\"la rochelle france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"218\" height=\"338\" alt=\"la rochelle france\" class=\"wp-image-62006 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\" data-sr